    "description": {
      "zh": "消防员头盔具有独特的火焰防护功能，其设计目的是确保消防员头部免受高温、机械冲击、腐蚀性环境和其他因灭火和进行紧急救行动而产生的危险和有害因素影响。",
      "en": "Firefighter helmet is an individual means of fire protection and is designed to ensure the protection of the firefighter's head from exposure to elevated temperatures, mechanical shocks, corrosive environments and other dangerous and harmful factors arising from extinguishing fires and conducting emergency rescue operations."
